Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我捏我捏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:20.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐好狠毒!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有新的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但隔壁的儲藏室裡好像有個老的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁那是我們社團的儲藏室嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我入社的時候  就已經基本不使用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,夢子老師或許不知道拿哪一把鑰匙開門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就問問小山老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,…喂  你們幹什麼呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這門真是不太好開…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…就這點程度  根本不算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,分明喘得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,進去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,空間大概是活動室的一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,窗戶也不方便打開…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  日光燈也打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還是趁早趕緊找到它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,畫得真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  好好找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這漫畫真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我小學時候讀過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  社長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜託你們關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得好緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看到沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你這副得意的表情是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這根本不算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,先別提這個  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是和內卷同處一室…你也可千萬別因此失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,失控?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀…門一關就變熱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還是得通通風才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,…咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得緊也不至於…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,居然這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是是  是我小看你了  對不起  行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不該說你孱弱無力  骨瘦如柴  面色蒼白!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…你沒說得這麼嚴重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  既然要道歉  就得更加有誠意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這箱子上寫著「石膏像」三個字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊  宇佐美同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  快來開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,比一開始卡得更緊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,應該得怪你當時錘了一下門吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?  又成我的錯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我臉上沾了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好近!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…呼出的氣息…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,輕叩著我的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是可蕾特同學的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐他們回去了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她把老師叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  聽得見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這扇門打不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天色這麼晚了  我也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  手機呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒戲  在包裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要到放學時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷…如  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒有人注意到我們  該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,既然門打不開  也只得維持現狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的情況就是在這裡住一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(457.998,381.763)\frz248.5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs40\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(460.998,407.763)\frz250.7}··
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦  如果繼續變冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,別突然這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?  很暖和吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你從剛才開始就在說些什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,天已經黑透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼蹲在角落裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  怎麼可能沒感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在慌死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…在這又小又黑的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,直到明早  都得二人…獨處…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,會起灰的  別打滾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學你沒事吧  剛才就怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,當然有事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆得在這裡過一晚哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都開始胡思亂想那種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,社長說的那句話還怎麼反駁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,內…內卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我可是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就給你看看我家甜心的厲害之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,摁下這個按鈕  眼睛就會發光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  真亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是我第一次覺得內卷你的手辦厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣做的話  或許會讓夜值巡邏的老師注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是又得好好巡邏才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊  夢子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  果然還是太黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那道光是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒人在才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,記得是這間來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才聽到什麼聲音了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你也聽到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪之類的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是以前社員的紀念照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?  是照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  窗戶這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像是一張臉?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說過讓你別嚇唬我了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再這樣我就把這個給折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,比妖怪還可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你還來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嚇唬你啦  你看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這裡應該是這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是門吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,從位置上看  另一邊就是活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  你把那邊的箱子移開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害  原來這裡相連在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好可蕾特同學沒有把門鎖上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果就那樣待了一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他們以後會怎麼捉弄我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了石膏像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我來搬石膏像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽打了好多通電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老師  您為何會在這種地方睡覺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是現在還是以前都會有人對石膏像塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz278\pos(183.998,137.763)}賢弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz262\pos(614.998,193.763)}大哥喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz334\pos(183.998,204.763)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\pos(587.998,255.763)\frz336.9}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和短髮波波頭合起來就是…波啵午安!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧  很有趣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這本漫畫也好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這本我也看過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這本很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,女主角有超能力的那一部對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,必殺技非常帥氣  像這樣…啪啪噼里啪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這間隱藏房間真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,既可以盡情看漫畫又能夠放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你隨時過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看起來聊得很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做功課  所以可以請你們安靜一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  功課在家裡做不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們安靜一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.07,Comment,,0,0,0,,你到底想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我不就不知道你們在做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?  那當然是在看漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太安靜的話總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼夾在漫畫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,寶物的所在之處?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,給未來的美術社員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}俺有一寶貝疙瘩  就藏在咱校園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吾有秘寶  藏於黌門之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}看你們能解開謎題  去挖出寶貝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,望爾等窺破機關以繼承秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}希望俺這寶貝能找個好人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,若蒙菩薩心腸者得之  善哉善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害  是尋寶遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要玩玩看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要玩  我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來剛好宇佐美同學就自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也能夠方便她集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們趕快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,到了休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在剛好是休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,暗號1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「離開活動室並前往紳士的小屋」上面這麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,紳士的小屋是指哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是腦筋急轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,順帶一提暗號2是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「前往從紳士的小屋的窗戶看得見的這個地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我覺得至少是有窗戶的房間才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是指男廁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,的確很「紳士」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這裡就麻煩內卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因為身為淑女的我們是不能進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  淑女?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是了個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是了個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,從窗戶看得見的這的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一封奇怪的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼特別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(555,660)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(685,660)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣子想出來也不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候就是普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方  這個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(663,660)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是「這」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(760,660)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  確實是這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  下個提示是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,暗號3 「找出字母」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?  就這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,問題來了  登登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡來看的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是U
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行  伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我腦筋急轉彎淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個  暗號4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「從找到的字母的末端開始  前進?步」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「?步」?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,U的末端是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,步數是從1853到1890的向日葵的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道答案是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  還不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,給一個提示  給一個提示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她很享受謎題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,提示  這是關於梵高的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(520,660)}Gogh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是什麼來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}註：日語中「梵高」和「五步」的發音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,1步  2步  3步  4步  5步!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉不是美術社員也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…內卷你來告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是1853出生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1890過世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他是荷蘭的畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,畫家?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說暗號4的答案是梵高畫過的向日葵的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有1幅燒毀了  但是一共有7幅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是7步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密寶物一定就在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  無論怎麼努力  這裡也不像是能挖的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看來沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼能挖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(710,660)}岡格尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,出現吧  永恆之槍!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}註：Gungnir  岡格尼爾  北歐神話中主神奧丁所使用的武器  是矮人族用世界之樹的樹枝打造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好短!  永恆之槍好短!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  憑我的魔力這就是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就只有前端而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有寫古文字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  畢竟是永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便丟也能挖?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,行了別鬧了  好了別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,體力勞動就交給就交給內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好像挖到什麼堅硬的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆之槍也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我們就來進行開封儀式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,無論有什麼  都由我們三等分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我不是美術社員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是我們三人找到的  這是當然的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們重要的冒險證明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,色情…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,死零之書對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,各位也有在勤奮作畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.35,0:23:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀?  社長呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原來在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來…那邊的房間有很多書對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓我幫忙找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  這個美術社大有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,魔導書和再次的散步  敬請期待
